6w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ian_mckellen_2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ian_mckellen_2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ian-mckellen">Ian McKellen</a> has encouraged young gay actors to come out, arguing that it is “silly” to be in the closet.</p><p> The veteran stage and screen actor has given an interview to <a href="https://www.thetimes.com/magazines/culture-magazine/article/ian-mckellen-being-in-the-closet-is-silly-hq35cdcpl" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>The Times</i></a> in which he discusses the experience he had when he himself revealed publicly that he was gay in 1988, at the age of 48.</p><p>他说：“我从未见过任何后悔的人。” “我为任何觉得自己无法出来的名人感到抱歉。在壁橱里很愚蠢 - 没有必要。不要听你的顾问，听你的心。听你更了解的同性恋朋友。出来。进入阳光。”</p><p> The <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/the-lord-of-the-rings"><i>Lord Of The Rings</i></a> star compared the situation to the English Premier League, which has never seen an openly LGBTQ+ senior player.他说：“在妇女运动中，这不是问题。” “我想，年轻的足球运动员可能像演员一样，从担心自己的收入的特工那里得到非常糟糕的建议。” </p><figure id="attachment_3771305" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3771305" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3771305" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Ian-McKellen-CREDIT-Photo-by-Dave-Benett_Getty-Images-for-The-Wolseley-Hospitality-Group.jpg" alt="伊恩·麦凯伦（Ian McKellen）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Ian-McKellen-CREDIT-Photo-by-Dave-Benett_Getty-Images-for-The-Wolseley-Hospitality-Group.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Ian-McKellen-CREDIT-Photo-by-Dave-Benett_Getty-Images-for-The-Wolseley-Hospitality-Group-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Ian-McKellen-CREDIT-Photo-by-Dave-Benett_Getty-Images-for-The-Wolseley-Hospitality-Group-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Ian-McKellen-CREDIT-Photo-by-Dave-Benett_Getty-Images-for-The-Wolseley-Hospitality-Group-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Ian-McKellen-CREDIT-Photo-by-Dave-Benett_Getty-Images-for-The-Wolseley-Hospitality-Group-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Ian-McKellen-CREDIT-Photo-by-Dave-Benett_Getty-Images-for-The-Wolseley-Hospitality-Group-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3771305" class="wp-caption-text">伊恩·麦凯伦（Ian McKellen） - 信用：沃尔斯利酒店集团（Wolseley Hospitality Group）的Dave Benett/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> “但是，第一个出场的英超足球运动员将成为世界上最著名的足球运动员，所有机构都乞求他的产品名称。”</p><p> McKellen, 85, was on stage in the West End in a production of <i>Player Kings</i> last summer when <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/ian-mckellen-expected-to-make-speedy-and-full-recovery-after-falling-off-stage-during-london-performance-3766379">he lost his footing and fell from the stage</a> . He was rushed to hospital and later confirmed <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/ian-mckellen-gives-hopeful-update-recovery-stage-fall-3766800">he had fractured his wrist</a> , rendering him <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/ian-mckellen-miss-play-remaining-london-shows-due-to-injuries-3767293">unable to fulfil the remaining dates of the play&#39;s run</a> .</p><p> Months later, he revealed that <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/ian-mckellen-dealing-with-agonising-pain-after-stage-fall-i-avoid-going-out-3785306">he was still dealing with “agonising pain”</a> from the accident, but <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/ian-mckellen-is-not-retiring-and-has-been-approached-to-play-gandalf-again-in-new-film-3789762">he did confirm that he had no plans to retire</a> .</p><p> He has also recently stated that if the character of Gandalf was set to appear in any future <i>Lord Of The Rings</i> films, he wanted to return to the role. “I&#39;m not letting anyone else put on the pointy hat and beard if I can help it,” he said, having played Gandalf in both <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/peter-jackson">Peter Jackson</a> &#39;s <i>Lord Of The Rings</i> films and the prequel <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-various-artists-15843-320647"><i>Hobbit</i></a> trilogy.</p><p> A new film, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/a-new-lord-of-the-rings-film-from-peter-jackson-is-coming-in-2026-3754902"><i>The Hunt For Gollum</i></a> , is due for release in 2026 with Andy Serkis set to direct and star in the new film. “Enthusiasm for <i>The Lord of the Rings</i> shows no sign of abating,” McKellen told the <i>Big Issue</i> recently. “我不能告诉你。我刚刚被告知会有更多的电影，甘道夫将参与其中，他们希望我会扮演他。”</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/ian-mckellen-encourages-young-gay-actors-to-come-out-being-in-the-closet-is-silly-3844802">Ian McKellen encourages young gay actors to come out: “Being in the closet is silly”</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
